import React from "react";
import { Form, Modal } from "react-bootstrap";
export default function ContactModal(){
    return(
        <>
        <Modal.Header closeButton>
            Create Button
        </Modal.Header>
        <Modal.Body>
            <Form>
                <From.Group>
                    <Form.Label>
                        Enter Your ID
                    </Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control type="text" required/>
                </From.Group>
            </Form>
        </Modal.Body>
        
        </>
    )
}
